{"parentUuid":"a24e3c6e-7f05-4576-86d2-ac5087c0395a","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NwxLVtdoNrpA3Cyu8zDGSh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`rand.Read(b)` の戻り値 `n` は**読み込んだバイト数**です。\n\nただし、`rand.Read` は **常に `len(b)` を返します**。つまり渡したスライスの長さと必ず一致するので、`n` をチェックする意味はほぼありません。\n\n```go\nb := make([]byte, 32)\nn, err := rand.Read(b)\n// n は必ず 32\n// err は必ず nil\n```\n\n`io.Reader` インターフェースの実装として形式上 `n` を返しているだけです。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":490,"cache_read_input_tokens":17578,"output_tokens":171,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":490},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZqKeAYqNZfkP4gXR9tm7","type":"assistant","uuid":"9d7d426d-2281-4b7e-bccb-f27669f7be67","timestamp":"2026-04-08T00:01:41.007Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku-ws1","sessionId":"552ce611-d7bb-4df9-a63f-c37a6d7a4eed","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"hashed-api-key-entity"}
